{
  "id": "adv_event_2108_01_04",
  "title": "花火大会のジンクス",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "……結局、今日は一日遊んだだけで\n終わってしまいましたわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ we just played all day\nand ended up with nothing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.633333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "はしゃぎ過ぎちゃったね\nみんなといると、楽しくてつい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We had too much fun.\nWhen I’m with you all‚ it’s so much fun‚ it just…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.833333333333333,
      "endTime": 11.233333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "私もよ\nでも、こういう一日もいいと思った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Me too.\nI think it’s nice having a day like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.433333333333334,
      "endTime": 16,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。それに、フェスに参加するために最近ずっと\n根を詰めてましたから……いいお休みになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. And‚ we’ve been overworking lately to perform at the festival‚\nso today was a good break.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.2,
      "endTime": 24.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "うんうん、芽衣ちゃん、\nこれからみんなでまた考えよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Mei-chan‚\nlet’s all think about it again‚ together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.633333333333333,
      "endTime": 28.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "ううっ、ありがとう。みんな優しいな\n芽衣、これからもっと真剣に頑張るよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you‚ you’re all so kind.\nFrom now on‚ I’m going to be way more serious about trying harder.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.166666666666668,
      "endTime": 39.06666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_fireworks-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9233.33333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、今日って……\n星見市の花火大会だったっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come to think of it‚ isn’t today\nHoshimi City’s fireworks show?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.266666666666666,
      "endTime": 44.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに大きな花火大会ではありませんけど\n……私は、好きですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s not that big of a display‚\nbut I like it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.333333333333336,
      "endTime": 51.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、みんな知ってる？\nこの花火大会、ジンクスがあるらしいんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ have you heard?\nApparently this firework display has a magical story about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9,
      "endTime": 58.199999999999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "この海岸で花火が上がっている間に、意中の異性に\n告白すると――うまくいく、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you confess your love to your romantic interest as the fireworks fly on this coast‚\nit’ll all go well‚ apparently.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.43333333333333,
      "endTime": 68.65398318809375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなんだ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.86666666666666,
      "endTime": 71.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、じゃあ、今、この瞬間にも\n殿方が好きな女性に、愛の告白を……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So if a man confesses his love at this moment\nto his beloved girl…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.96666666666667,
      "endTime": 80.16666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "逆に、女の子の方からの告白もあるかも！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or maybe from the girl!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.36666666666666,
      "endTime": 84.10521546999612,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな……女性から……！\n渚ちゃん、大胆なことを言い出すのね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Re-really‚ from the girl?!\nNagisa-chan‚ that’s a pretty bold thing to say…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.3,
      "endTime": 90.52893392389471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、そう考えながら見てるとドキドキしちゃうね\n琴乃ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just thinking that while I watch the fireworks‚ my heart flutters.\nKotono-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.73333333333333,
      "endTime": 97.43333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yeah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.63333333333334,
      "endTime": 99.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "…………\nそうだよね、女の子から行動してもいいんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…\nYou’re right‚ it’s okay for the girl to make the first move.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.83333333333333,
      "endTime": 107.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.66666666666667,
      "endTime": 109.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "花火……恋人……\n月明り……告白……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fireworks… lover…\nMoonlight… love confessions…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.8,
      "endTime": 116.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたの？　芽衣",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What’s up‚ Mei-chan?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.13333333333334,
      "endTime": 118.86319726308187,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "閃いたよ！　みんな\n芽衣達の、月のテンペストの夏！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve got it. All of you!\nOur Moon Tempest Summer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.06666666666666,
      "endTime": 124.5238021492958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "花火の下で、告白する女の子の歌？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A song of a girl confessing her love under the fireworks?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.83333333333333,
      "endTime": 130.94453514417012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "そう！　ず～っと好きだったんだけど\nその想いを伝えられなかった女の子が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! She’s liked a boy for a really long time‚\nbut never been able to express her feelings…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.13333333333333,
      "endTime": 138.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "勇気を出して花火が消えるまでに\n告白しようって決心するの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She then decides to be brave and\ntell him before the fireworks are over!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.43333333333334,
      "endTime": 143.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "女性の方から告白するなんて、芽衣も見かけによら――\nいえ、芽衣ならさらっと言えそうですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The girl confessing her love first? You can’t judge Mei by appearances—\nOr actually‚ that just sounds like what Mei would do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.4,
      "endTime": 152.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "きっとそんなことないよ。もし本当に好きな人が\n出来たら、芽衣だって絶対緊張すると思うな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not at all true. If there was someone I really liked‚\nI’m sure I’d be really tense.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.7,
      "endTime": 161.3486211504255,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "だから、同じような気持ちの子の背中を\n押してあげられる……そんな歌がいいと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So I think it would be good to have a song that would\nencourage a girl who felt that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.56666666666666,
      "endTime": 169.23333333333335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、芽衣ちゃん、もしかしたら誰か\n気になる人がいるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe‚ Mei-chan‚ is there someone\nthat you like?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.43333333333334,
      "endTime": 175.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2108_01_04-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "ないない！　いないよ！\n芽衣には今、恋してるヒマなんてないもん！",
